<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>个人主页 - 肇中2025</title>
    <link href="/lib/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/lib/fontawesome/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #f59e0b;
            --cork: #d97706;
            --warm-bg: #fcfaf7;
            --text-primary: #1e293b;
            --text-secondary: #64748b;
        }

        body {
            font-family: "Noto Sans SC", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--warm-bg);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            padding-top: 70px;
        }

        .warm-nav {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 60px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(241, 245, 249, 0.8);
            z-index: 1030;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .nav-brand {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        
        .btn-warm {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--cork));
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <nav class="warm-nav">
        <div class="container d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
            <a href="/" class="nav-brand">
                <i class="fas fa-graduation-cap text-warning"></i>
                <span class="nav-brand-text">肇中2025</span>
            </a>
            <a href="javascript:history.back()" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm">返回</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container py-4">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4">
                    <div class="card-body p-4">
                        <div class="text-center mb-4">
                            <div class="rounded-circle bg-warning bg-opacity-10 d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mb-3"
                                style="width: 80px; height: 80px;">
                                <i class="fas fa-user fa-2x text-warning"></i>
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="fw-bold"><%= user.username %></h3>
                        </div>

                        <div class="list-group list-group-flush mb-4 rounded-3">
                            <div class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center p-3">
                                <span class="text-muted">身份</span>
                                <span class="fw-medium"><%= user.school_type %>生</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center p-3">
                                <span class="text-muted">校区</span>
                                <span class="fw-medium"><%= user.campus %></span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center p-3">
                                <span class="text-muted">年级</span>
                                <span class="fw-medium"><%= user.graduation_year %>届 <%= user.class_name %></span>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <% if (user.isCollegeStudent) { %>
                            <div class="bg-primary bg-opacity-10 p-4 rounded-3 mb-4">
                                <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
                                    <i class="fas fa-university text-primary me-2"></i>
                                    <h5 class="mb-0 text-primary fw-bold">大学生认证</h5>
                                </div>
                                <p class="small text-muted mb-3">
                                    您已从肇中毕业，欢迎认证您的大学信息。
                                    <br>认证后，在咨询区回复贴子时将展示您的大学名称，为学弟学妹提供参考。
                                </p>
                                <form action="/profile/update" method="POST">
                                    <div class="form-floating mb-3">
                                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="university" name="university" 
                                            placeholder="请输入您的大学名称" value="<%= user.university || '' %>">
                                        <label for="university">就读大学（如：北京大学）</label>
                                    </div>
                                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary w-100">
                                        Update / 更新信息
                                    </button>
                                </form>
                            </div>
                        <% } %>

                        <div class="d-grid gap-2">
                            <a href="/my-codes" class="btn btn-outline-warning">
                                <i class="fas fa-ticket-alt me-2"></i>我的邀请码
                            </a>
                            <form action="/logout" method="POST" class="d-grid">
                                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-outline-danger">退出登录</button>
                            </form>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="/lib/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
